1
00:00:22,986 --> 00:00:28,976
♪Remembering the old days in a trance♪

2
00:00:29,326 --> 00:00:36,136
♪We are destined to fight together♪

3
00:00:36,416 --> 00:00:43,116
♪The past has gone but the memory lasts♪

4
00:00:43,436 --> 00:00:50,456
♪Our happiness and sorrow
in the good old days♪

5
00:00:50,666 --> 00:00:57,296
♪The journey is difficult,
through the crowds, to the end of time♪

6
00:00:57,616 --> 00:01:05,816
♪I'm brave and undefeatable♪

7
00:01:06,536 --> 00:01:13,566
♪The sky has become dark
and the birds have returned home♪

8
00:01:13,726 --> 00:01:20,776
♪Breaking all obstacles
and reaching the peak above the clouds♪

9
00:01:20,926 --> 00:01:27,776
♪Watching the thin plumes of smoke
and the beautiful scenery♪

10
00:01:27,936 --> 00:01:31,246
♪Working together,
overcoming all difficulties♪

11
00:01:31,516 --> 00:01:35,676
♪I will be known as the fearless one♪

12
00:01:35,676 --> 00:01:39,796
=Douluo Continent=

13
00:01:39,876 --> 00:01:42,836
=Episode 39=

14
00:03:08,640 --> 00:03:09,200
You're here.

15
00:03:13,480 --> 00:03:14,039
Dad.

16
00:03:15,200 --> 00:03:16,120
It's really you.

17
00:03:19,920 --> 00:03:21,879
You are the mastermind behind everything?

18
00:03:22,679 --> 00:03:23,879
Why are you shocked?

19
00:03:25,200 --> 00:03:26,440
You want to assassinate Bi Bi Dong

20
00:03:26,720 --> 00:03:27,840
for revenge?

21
00:03:28,319 --> 00:03:28,879
Yes.

22
00:03:29,679 --> 00:03:31,120
You have

23
00:03:32,679 --> 00:03:34,120
controlled Cang Hui School,

24
00:03:34,840 --> 00:03:35,879
poisoned Du Gu Bo,

25
00:03:35,879 --> 00:03:36,920
and threatened Qibao Amber Clan?

26
00:03:37,440 --> 00:03:38,480
I can't kill Bi Bi Dong

27
00:03:39,039 --> 00:03:40,280
alone.

28
00:03:43,120 --> 00:03:44,599
You also

29
00:03:44,599 --> 00:03:45,519
enhanced the mutation of Martial Souls?

30
00:03:46,080 --> 00:03:47,759
I need more forces.

31
00:03:49,679 --> 00:03:51,200
But the process of creating Mutant Souls

32
00:03:51,200 --> 00:03:52,280
harmed a lot of people.

33
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:54,679
Ma Hong Jun's dad died because of that too.

34
00:03:55,319 --> 00:03:56,640
I'll compensate Ma Hong Jun

35
00:03:57,360 --> 00:03:58,599
after I kill Bi Bi Dong.

36
00:03:59,920 --> 00:04:00,519
Dad,

37
00:04:00,920 --> 00:04:01,840
this is not a problem

38
00:04:01,840 --> 00:04:03,120
that can be settled by compensation.

39
00:04:03,840 --> 00:04:04,519
Someone has to sacrifice

40
00:04:04,799 --> 00:04:05,920
for a big enterprise.

41
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:11,399
I didn't expect

42
00:04:12,640 --> 00:04:14,080
you would become a person like this.

43
00:04:15,039 --> 00:04:15,640
How am I now?

44
00:04:17,360 --> 00:04:19,480
Why did you look for me?

45
00:04:20,399 --> 00:04:22,440
Cang Hui must enter the final.

46
00:04:23,239 --> 00:04:23,919
Why?

47
00:04:25,040 --> 00:04:26,600
The last step can only be taken

48
00:04:27,479 --> 00:04:28,919
when Cang Hui becomes the champion.

49
00:04:34,199 --> 00:04:35,040
For the champion,

50
00:04:35,799 --> 00:04:37,320
Bi Bi Dong will present the award in person.

51
00:04:50,840 --> 00:04:52,440
I found

52
00:04:53,320 --> 00:04:54,840
a special Mutant Soul.

53
00:04:55,399 --> 00:04:56,519
His only Soul Skill

54
00:04:57,160 --> 00:04:58,399
is Blank Space.

55
00:05:00,359 --> 00:05:01,239
He can only use

56
00:05:01,239 --> 00:05:03,840
his Soul Skill once in a lifetime.

57
00:05:04,199 --> 00:05:06,120
He'll die after using it.

58
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:07,840
This is a Soul Skill

59
00:05:08,160 --> 00:05:09,880
performed by one's life.

60
00:05:10,720 --> 00:05:11,799
The only strength of this Soul Skill

61
00:05:12,079 --> 00:05:13,399
is to make the people

62
00:05:13,720 --> 00:05:14,959
in proximity

63
00:05:15,799 --> 00:05:17,519
lose control of their power.

64
00:05:19,440 --> 00:05:20,679
What is the use of the arrow then?

65
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:21,880
It works like a sign.

66
00:05:22,479 --> 00:05:23,239
So that his strength

67
00:05:23,720 --> 00:05:25,000
can be released with a target.

68
00:05:25,639 --> 00:05:26,639
His target

69
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:28,959
will only be Bi Bi Dong.

70
00:05:29,320 --> 00:05:30,959
But, Bi Bi Dong may not come close to him.

71
00:05:31,239 --> 00:05:32,479
Therefore, I have prepared

72
00:05:32,479 --> 00:05:33,799
a few more people for her.

73
00:05:35,160 --> 00:05:38,079
First, it's Spear of Void.

74
00:05:41,679 --> 00:05:42,959
A Soul Sect with Quadruple Soul Rings

75
00:05:43,120 --> 00:05:45,160
cannot harm the chief of Martial Soul Hall.

76
00:05:46,040 --> 00:05:47,120
He just needs

77
00:05:47,120 --> 00:05:48,440
to block the vision.

78
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:54,479
Mutant Soul, Returning Mirror.

79
00:05:55,079 --> 00:05:56,040
It can exchange spaces.

80
00:05:56,440 --> 00:05:57,679
It's effective on humans too.

81
00:06:02,519 --> 00:06:03,840
Bi Bi Dong will lose

82
00:06:04,840 --> 00:06:06,440
her spirit control over Soul Power

83
00:06:06,880 --> 00:06:08,560
in a very short period.

84
00:06:20,679 --> 00:06:21,760
My final preparation

85
00:06:23,440 --> 00:06:26,399
is Mutant Soul, Space Isolation.

86
00:06:27,040 --> 00:06:27,840
His Soul Skill

87
00:06:28,079 --> 00:06:29,479
has no offensive ability.

88
00:06:29,679 --> 00:06:31,160
It can only block all the assistance

89
00:06:31,160 --> 00:06:32,320
in a short period.

90
00:06:33,320 --> 00:06:33,959
Then,

91
00:06:34,600 --> 00:06:36,600
it's those Grand Soul Land Masters
that I've prepared.

92
00:06:37,880 --> 00:06:39,359
If we block all the assistance,

93
00:06:39,919 --> 00:06:41,679
how can those Grand Soul Land Masters
get in the arena?

94
00:06:42,959 --> 00:06:43,600
What do you think?

95
00:06:46,320 --> 00:06:46,919
Returning Mirror.

96
00:07:14,840 --> 00:07:15,840
This is the best time

97
00:07:16,239 --> 00:07:17,840
for all the Grand Soul Land Masters

98
00:07:17,919 --> 00:07:19,280
to take action.

99
00:07:19,720 --> 00:07:21,239
Bi Bi Dong is really strong.

100
00:07:22,359 --> 00:07:22,760
But,

101
00:07:22,760 --> 00:07:25,079
under the successive attacks,

102
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:27,079
she'll lose control over her Martial Soul.

103
00:07:27,440 --> 00:07:28,359
She'll definitely die.

104
00:07:29,600 --> 00:07:31,239
Why do we have to wait until after the final

105
00:07:31,519 --> 00:07:32,519
to implement this plan?

106
00:07:33,720 --> 00:07:35,120
Her position is high.

107
00:07:35,919 --> 00:07:37,359
Normally, no one can get close to her.

108
00:07:37,840 --> 00:07:39,000
Only when she presents the award

109
00:07:39,519 --> 00:07:41,519
will she come close
to the students of Cang Hui alone.

110
00:07:41,880 --> 00:07:43,440
After all, they only have Quadruple Soul Rings.

111
00:07:43,880 --> 00:07:45,239
She won't be too alert.

112
00:07:46,479 --> 00:07:47,919
The student who is going to use the arrow

113
00:07:48,199 --> 00:07:49,079
will die.

114
00:07:49,479 --> 00:07:50,479
Actually,

115
00:07:51,239 --> 00:07:52,600
all the students of Cang Hui

116
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:53,959
will die.

117
00:07:55,239 --> 00:07:56,959
Is it worth it to let many people die

118
00:07:57,359 --> 00:07:58,720
only to kill the chief of Martial Soul Hall?

119
00:07:59,120 --> 00:08:01,199
Bi Bi Dong is the chief of Martial Soul Hall.

120
00:08:02,000 --> 00:08:03,519
She's the Greatest Soul Master
in Douluo Continent.

121
00:08:03,799 --> 00:08:04,600
It's impossible to kill her

122
00:08:04,720 --> 00:08:05,639
without any sacrifice.

123
00:08:08,079 --> 00:08:09,079
I can't accept it.

124
00:08:09,120 --> 00:08:10,079
You don't have to do anything.

125
00:08:10,760 --> 00:08:12,600
You just have to allow
Cang Hui School to enter the final.

126
00:08:14,000 --> 00:08:15,399
How is it possible for them

127
00:08:15,399 --> 00:08:16,919
to defeat Martial Soul Hall's Battle Team?

128
00:08:17,479 --> 00:08:18,199
I'll arrange it.

129
00:08:18,799 --> 00:08:20,440
You just have to convince your teammates.

130
00:08:23,880 --> 00:08:26,320
It's wrong to do those things.

131
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:28,040
I'm your dad.

132
00:08:28,720 --> 00:08:29,600
I'll not hurt you.

133
00:08:31,880 --> 00:08:32,560
I refuse to obey.

134
00:08:33,440 --> 00:08:34,120
Actually,

135
00:08:35,040 --> 00:08:36,160
I have other ways

136
00:08:36,639 --> 00:08:37,720
to solve the problem.

137
00:08:41,679 --> 00:08:42,200
Tang San!

138
00:08:46,760 --> 00:08:48,000
We didn't see you come back after a while,

139
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:48,719
so we came here.

140
00:08:49,279 --> 00:08:50,200
Is he the mastermind?

141
00:08:51,359 --> 00:08:52,039
Wait a minute.

142
00:08:52,359 --> 00:08:53,159
Protect Tang San.

143
00:08:59,599 --> 00:09:00,640
Kill them now.

144
00:09:01,120 --> 00:09:02,560
Cang Hui can also enter the final!

145
00:09:03,359 --> 00:09:05,520
Stop it!

146
00:09:10,279 --> 00:09:10,839
Brother Dai!

147
00:09:11,599 --> 00:09:12,039
Dad!

148
00:09:15,440 --> 00:09:16,039
Ou Si Ke.

149
00:09:18,440 --> 00:09:19,320
Stop it!

150
00:09:19,400 --> 00:09:20,479
Wu, step aside!

151
00:09:23,560 --> 00:09:24,960
Zhu Zhu Qing!

152
00:09:38,479 --> 00:09:38,839
Dad!

153
00:09:40,440 --> 00:09:41,919
Dad, stop it, please.

154
00:09:42,159 --> 00:09:43,120
Let's go back to the Saint of Soul Village.

155
00:09:43,359 --> 00:09:44,039
You'll be the ironsmith.

156
00:09:44,799 --> 00:09:45,679
I'm your son.

157
00:09:45,960 --> 00:09:47,039
We'll stay together.

158
00:09:47,880 --> 00:09:49,000
Give up the struggle.

159
00:09:49,440 --> 00:09:50,760
Let me decide for you.

160
00:10:29,320 --> 00:10:30,400
If you quit the contest,

161
00:10:31,120 --> 00:10:32,320
I'll spare her.

162
00:10:35,880 --> 00:10:36,440
No need.

163
00:10:37,640 --> 00:10:38,440
You can kill her.

164
00:10:38,679 --> 00:10:39,080
What?

165
00:10:39,839 --> 00:10:41,120
She's not Wu.

166
00:10:42,400 --> 00:10:43,440
You're not my dad.

167
00:10:50,760 --> 00:10:52,359
When did I fall into your trap?

168
00:10:53,159 --> 00:10:54,200
Teacher Shi Nian.

169
00:10:56,000 --> 00:10:57,640
If I had given up everything

170
00:10:57,880 --> 00:10:59,159
and followed your arrangement,

171
00:10:59,880 --> 00:11:00,679
I would have been

172
00:11:00,679 --> 00:11:01,760
controlled by you, right?

173
00:11:02,719 --> 00:11:03,760
What are you talking about?

174
00:11:04,440 --> 00:11:04,960
The wind chime.

175
00:11:05,239 --> 00:11:05,679
What?

176
00:11:06,760 --> 00:11:08,000
The wind chime is the symbol of home

177
00:11:08,679 --> 00:11:09,799
to my dad and me.

178
00:11:10,359 --> 00:11:11,839
It represents the love of my dad to me.

179
00:11:12,640 --> 00:11:14,640
He won't destroy this love.

180
00:11:16,919 --> 00:11:18,120
So, you can only create

181
00:11:18,120 --> 00:11:18,919
their figures,

182
00:11:19,560 --> 00:11:20,960
but you can't know about my memory.

183
00:11:23,120 --> 00:11:23,960
Let me think.

184
00:11:25,479 --> 00:11:27,320
You didn't speak to me voluntarily.

185
00:11:27,960 --> 00:11:28,960
I spoke first.

186
00:11:29,799 --> 00:11:30,880
Therefore, you knew

187
00:11:31,279 --> 00:11:32,719
that Hao Tian Soul Master is my dad.

188
00:11:44,679 --> 00:11:45,960
Since you saw me

189
00:11:45,960 --> 00:11:47,239
in Shi Lan Ke's lodging,

190
00:11:48,400 --> 00:11:50,159
I've trapped you in a dream.

191
00:11:50,599 --> 00:11:51,560
You're right.

192
00:11:52,159 --> 00:11:53,560
When you're in despair

193
00:11:53,719 --> 00:11:55,120
and admit your failure,

194
00:11:55,560 --> 00:11:56,839
you'll be controlled by me.

195
00:11:57,679 --> 00:11:59,239
Therefore, your plan failed.

196
00:11:59,479 --> 00:12:00,400
Not yet.

197
00:12:01,359 --> 00:12:03,239
There's a more troublesome plan.

198
00:12:03,719 --> 00:12:04,839
It's to kill you repeatedly

199
00:12:05,120 --> 00:12:06,919
in your dream.

200
00:12:07,400 --> 00:12:08,520
To torture you

201
00:12:09,359 --> 00:12:11,320
until you lose all your hope.

202
00:12:12,120 --> 00:12:12,880
Then,

203
00:12:13,679 --> 00:12:15,000
I'll still be able to control you.

204
00:12:16,120 --> 00:12:16,719
It's useless.

205
00:12:17,320 --> 00:12:18,320
You are no match for me

206
00:12:18,919 --> 00:12:21,560
even in the dream.

207
00:12:28,679 --> 00:12:30,120
Although I need to waste more time,

208
00:12:30,880 --> 00:12:32,159
the result will still be the same.

209
00:12:34,120 --> 00:12:35,520
I didn't expect

210
00:12:35,880 --> 00:12:38,159
that you're the son of Hao Tian Soul Master.

211
00:12:39,039 --> 00:12:40,279
So, my dad is not the one

212
00:12:40,279 --> 00:12:41,120
behind Cang Hui.

213
00:12:41,560 --> 00:12:43,320
The mastermind is
the Grand Chrysanthemum Master.

214
00:12:44,440 --> 00:12:45,919
You asked too much.

215
00:12:46,799 --> 00:12:48,000
Are you ready

216
00:12:48,000 --> 00:12:49,760
to die in pain repeatedly?

217
00:13:09,440 --> 00:13:10,039
What is this?

218
00:13:12,679 --> 00:13:14,080
Who hid such great power

219
00:13:14,080 --> 00:13:15,000
in your heart?

220
00:13:16,279 --> 00:13:17,239
(Tang San.)

221
00:13:20,080 --> 00:13:21,400
This is the power of the Grand Soul Land Master.

222
00:13:23,479 --> 00:13:24,359
(Son.)

223
00:13:25,120 --> 00:13:26,679
(I left my final strength)

224
00:13:26,679 --> 00:13:28,000
(in your heart.)

225
00:13:28,520 --> 00:13:30,479
(Although I can't see you again,)

226
00:13:30,799 --> 00:13:32,839
(I'll always be with you)

227
00:13:33,440 --> 00:13:36,479
(and protect you until the end.)

228
00:13:36,479 --> 00:13:37,039
Mom.

229
00:13:45,719 --> 00:13:46,120
Hold on.

230
00:13:46,320 --> 00:13:46,799
Tang San,

231
00:13:46,960 --> 00:13:47,440
hold on!

232
00:13:48,039 --> 00:13:49,359
I'll tell you who the mastermind is.

233
00:13:49,479 --> 00:13:50,320
You let me go.

234
00:13:50,359 --> 00:13:53,200
Tang San...

235
00:14:11,760 --> 00:14:13,440
I broke his Mind Branch Martial Soul.

236
00:14:23,200 --> 00:14:24,400
Where are we?

237
00:14:26,479 --> 00:14:28,000
All of you are awake now?

238
00:14:37,760 --> 00:14:39,320
He became like this

239
00:14:40,120 --> 00:14:41,120
after his Mind Branch Martial Soul was broken.

240
00:14:41,719 --> 00:14:42,479
This should be the backlash effect

241
00:14:42,479 --> 00:14:43,919
of his Mind Branch Martial Soul.

242
00:14:46,039 --> 00:14:46,799
How did you break it?

243
00:14:48,159 --> 00:14:49,599
Everyone has a secret.

244
00:14:50,640 --> 00:14:52,159
I understand. I'll not ask anymore.

245
00:14:53,760 --> 00:14:54,479
Where are the rest?

246
00:14:55,320 --> 00:14:56,159
They're awake now.

247
00:14:56,799 --> 00:14:57,880
Their last memory

248
00:14:57,880 --> 00:14:59,560
remains the first time when they came to Cang Hui.

249
00:14:59,880 --> 00:15:00,960
It has been a long time.

250
00:15:02,000 --> 00:15:03,120
They can't get used to it.

251
00:15:04,640 --> 00:15:05,320
How about you?

252
00:15:05,919 --> 00:15:07,080
I plan to leave Martial Soul City

253
00:15:07,359 --> 00:15:08,159
with them.

254
00:15:09,000 --> 00:15:09,640
How about the contest?

255
00:15:09,960 --> 00:15:10,799
It's nothing.

256
00:15:11,599 --> 00:15:12,200
Thank you.

257
00:15:12,839 --> 00:15:14,359
We got rid of this demon finally.

258
00:15:15,520 --> 00:15:16,640
Do you plan to leave him here?

259
00:15:17,560 --> 00:15:18,400
I want to bring him with me.

260
00:15:19,560 --> 00:15:20,080
Revenge?

261
00:15:20,520 --> 00:15:20,960
No.

262
00:15:21,719 --> 00:15:22,560
I'm going to keep an eye on him

263
00:15:22,919 --> 00:15:24,000
and prevent him from waking up again.

264
00:15:25,479 --> 00:15:25,919
How about you?

265
00:15:27,239 --> 00:15:28,200
Although we have solved

266
00:15:28,400 --> 00:15:29,599
almost everything about Cang Hui School,

267
00:15:30,279 --> 00:15:32,000
the Grand Soul Land Master
behind Cang Hui

268
00:15:32,000 --> 00:15:32,960
is still out there.

269
00:15:33,719 --> 00:15:34,279
Moreover,

270
00:15:34,880 --> 00:15:35,960
the contest hasn't ended yet.

271
00:15:36,719 --> 00:15:37,919
Martial Soul Hall's Battle Team is too strong.

272
00:15:38,599 --> 00:15:40,440
I think it's hard for your team to win.

273
00:15:40,880 --> 00:15:41,919
We have to try.

274
00:15:43,359 --> 00:15:44,320
I wish that your team can win.

275
00:15:44,520 --> 00:15:44,919
Oh yes.

276
00:15:45,479 --> 00:15:46,560
When will you leave Martial Soul City?

277
00:15:46,679 --> 00:15:47,239
As soon as possible.

278
00:15:48,440 --> 00:15:49,120
We'll not send you off then.

279
00:15:52,239 --> 00:15:52,640
Tang San.

280
00:15:54,760 --> 00:15:56,599
Thank you. I am indebted to you.

281
00:15:59,760 --> 00:16:01,239
If you are in trouble in the future,

282
00:16:01,719 --> 00:16:02,320
come to me.

283
00:16:10,359 --> 00:16:11,640
What if Shi Nian wakes up again?

284
00:16:11,919 --> 00:16:13,279
If you face something like this in the future,

285
00:16:13,279 --> 00:16:14,039
you must bring me along.

286
