375
00:21:07,800 --> 00:21:09,160
who viewed "The Secret of Star".

376
00:21:09,400 --> 00:21:10,239
The Grand Chrysanthemum Master?

377
00:21:10,520 --> 00:21:11,239
It turns out

378
00:21:11,880 --> 00:21:13,559
that he's the spy in Martial Soul Hall.

379
00:21:16,559 --> 00:21:17,079
You said

380
00:21:17,079 --> 00:21:18,280
someone from the library had asked you

381
00:21:18,280 --> 00:21:19,319
about the view records?

382
00:21:22,079 --> 00:21:22,559
Yes.

383
00:21:23,880 --> 00:21:25,439
So, if I were the spy,

384
00:21:26,439 --> 00:21:27,439
I wouldn't use my token

385
00:21:27,439 --> 00:21:28,559
to investigate.

386
00:21:28,559 --> 00:21:29,079
Am I right?

387
00:21:30,280 --> 00:21:30,719
Yes.

388
00:21:30,959 --> 00:21:32,319
It'll be too obvious then.

389
00:21:33,400 --> 00:21:34,239
So, you think

390
00:21:34,599 --> 00:21:35,719
the Grand Chrysanthemum Master
may not be the spy?

391
00:21:37,800 --> 00:21:39,040
But, he indeed researched about Soul Beasts

392
00:21:39,040 --> 00:21:40,599
without the permission of Martial Soul Hall.

393
00:21:40,920 --> 00:21:41,920
But, researching about Soul Beasts

394
00:21:42,199 --> 00:21:42,760
doesn't mean

395
00:21:42,760 --> 00:21:43,959
he wants to kill
the chief of Martial Soul Hall, right?

396
00:21:45,239 --> 00:21:47,280
You said he was the spy yesterday.

397
00:21:47,680 --> 00:21:48,839
Today, you said it might not be the case.

398
00:21:49,319 --> 00:21:49,760
I'm thinking

399
00:21:50,280 --> 00:21:51,120
could it be that someone

400
00:21:51,319 --> 00:21:52,559
