468
00:24:57,760 --> 00:24:58,880
It's the Grand Ghost Master, right?

469
00:24:59,239 --> 00:25:00,400
He caught

470
00:25:00,400 --> 00:25:01,439
the people from the schools that had been out.

471
00:25:03,000 --> 00:25:05,599
