480
00:25:26,559 --> 00:25:28,040
After Cang Hui withdrew from the contest,

481
00:25:29,040 --> 00:25:30,680
your school will enter the final.

482
00:25:31,439 --> 00:25:32,280
To be honest,

483
00:25:33,120 --> 00:25:34,160
