489
00:25:51,040 --> 00:25:52,439
For the experiment,

490
00:25:53,319 --> 00:25:54,839
the interspace created

491
00:25:54,839 --> 00:25:56,439
by the Grand Chrysanthemum Master

492
00:25:58,439 --> 00:25:59,959
