544
00:28:36,000 --> 00:28:36,719
Lastly,

545
00:28:37,640 --> 00:28:38,400
protect yourself.

546
00:28:39,400 --> 00:28:40,400
Master is right.

547
00:28:42,000 --> 00:28:42,800
